               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Ātish'kadah by Āz̲ar</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh89005046 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2010105563 http://lccn.loc.gov/nr96004942" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_571-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic </textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Taz̲kirah assembling selections from poetic works and biographies of ancient and modern poets organised by various criteria (ethnicity, profession, region, and country, for example), written by <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656332.0x000001 viaf_118523950" role="aut">Luṭf ʿAlī ibn Āqā Khān takhalluṣ Āz̲ar</persName> (d. 1195/1780). 
                        </p>
                        <p>Dated colophon: completed by <persName key="person_f7128" role="scr">Gajpat Singh Khatrī</persName>, resident of Shāhjahānābād, for munshīʾ ṣāḥib <persName key="person_f8244" role="pat">Khvājah Zayn al-ʿĀbidīn Khān Ṣāḥib</persName>, Wednesday, 5 Shaʿbān in RY 17 on Emperor Muḥammad Akbar Shāh II, 1239/5 April 1824. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Minute nastaʿlīq. 
</p>
                        <p>Not foliated. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios torn and unbound. 
</p>
                        <p>Fragile. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_118523950">Āz̲ar</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_118523950">آذر</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_10055">Ātish'kadah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_10055">آتش كده</title>
                  </msItem>
